creator: Giftin Technologies
descriptionHtml:
Dual wordle is an interesting wordle puzzle game in which you will solve two words in one go. If you love word games and want to improve your vocabulary, this is the right game for you. Dual Wordle is a letter based game with 4 letters, 5 letters support. For every wordle puzzle you have 6 guesses. On each guess you will get to know what letters are at correct position, what letters are at wrong position and what letters are not at all part of the word hidden in the wordle puzzle.

If you get stuck in the middle, you can use the hint to reveal a letter of the word puzzle. This wordle game will become more interesting as you play. You can enjoy playing this game for hours.

If you cannot solve the wordle puzzle within the given tries, then the word hidden in the wordle puzzle will be revealed and you need to start the new level.

The beauty of this dual Wordl game is it maintains current winning streak and maximum winning streak which helps to motivate ourselves to beat our own record.

By playing this dual wordle game, you'll not only get yourselves challenged, you can learn lot of new words and improve your vocabulary.

descriptionHtml:
Are you a word puzzle enthusiast looking for a new challenge? Look no further than Word Challenge, the ultimate word puzzle game! With over 1000 levels, each with two hidden words to find in just 7 chances, you'll never run out of new puzzles to solve.

The game includes a crossword tile that displays hints by showing the correct letters as green. You can also use the hint option to reveal correct letters one by one. But be careful, because each hint you use will reduce your final score.

Compete against other players on the leaderboard, with weekly, daily, and all-time high scores. Show off your word puzzle skills and climb to the top of the rankings.

Word Challenge is perfect for fans of word games like Wordle, with challenging puzzles that will keep you coming back for more. Download Word Challenge now and put your word puzzle skills to the test!
